metadata.name: Nago of "Tsujiro"
metadata.description:
The current situation was very cruel. Nago had a single attack caused the Z gang to die instantly. Nago was a very vicious beast. It didn't ask for any reason. If someone invaded his home It will all end in death. Nago rarely shows up to anyone. but believe me It's good for everyone Because he was a beast that even beasts together would not be merciful to.

Charater : Nago , Z gang
Where : Nago field
Resolution : 2250 X 2250 
Animation : 72 Frame
Program : Aseprite
File : .Gif
Shades : Pink , Black , Purple

"Tsujiro" is the story of a demon in a dark dimension. These beasts are all evil. and with a strange face, if he saw a human He will kill without hesitation. Very few people are kind and don't mind killing humans. The story continues in this dark world.

! please don't make a sound If you meet them must be as quiet as possible
